data.news_body:
Pursuant to regulation 30 and 33 of the SEBI (Listing Obligations and Disclosure Requirements) Regulations, 2015, we have to inform you that the Board of Directors of the Company at their
meeting held today i.e. Tuesday, November 08, 2022, have considered and approved inter-alia:

your records.

2. 3rd Interim Dividend of 200% i.e. Rs. 2.00 (Rupees Two Only) per equity share of face value of Re.1/- during the financial year 2022-23 and has fixed Wednesday, November 16, 2022

Kindly take the same on record.
